{"word":"G4152 - πνευματικός - pneumatikós - pnyoo-mat-ik-os' - Spiritual","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πνευματικός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">pneumatikós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pnyoo-mat-ik-os'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Spiritual</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"ஆவிக்குரிய ஞான, ஆவிக்கேற்ற - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"1. relating to the human spirit"},{"paragraph":"2. belonging to a spirit"},{"paragraph":"3. belonging to the Divine Spirit"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4151 - πνεῦμα - pneûma - pnyoo'-mah/4151\">G4151</a>; <i>non-carnal</i>, that is, (humanly) <i>ethereal</i> (as opposed to gross), or (daemoniacally) a <i>spirit</i> (concretely), or (divinely) <i>supernatural</i>, <i>regenerate</i>, <i>religious</i>: - spiritual. Compare <a href=\"#/G5591 - ψυχικός - psychikós - psoo-khee-kos'/5591\">G5591</a>.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1606/1606\">G1606</a>, <a href=\"#/G2315/2315\">G2315</a>, <a href=\"#/G4151/4151\">G4151</a>, <a href=\"#/G4152/4152\">G4152</a>, <a href=\"#/G4153/4153\">G4153</a>, <a href=\"#/G4154/4154\">G4154</a>"}]}